    <h2>WHAT ARE THE SYMPTOMS OF THE CORONA VIRUS?</h2>
    <p>People who have been diagnosed with coronavirus exhibit symptoms similar to those of other viral respiratory infections.</p>
    <h3>The most common symptoms of COVID-19 are </h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Runny nose</li>
		<li>Headache</li>
		<li>Cough</li>
        <li>Sore throat</li>
        <li>Fever</li>
        <li>Shortness of breath</li>
	</ul>
